<bibRefCitation author="Ingrisch" box="[151,465,188,213]" pageId="3" pageNumber="282" refString="Ingrisch, S. &amp; Shishodia, M. S. (1998) New species and records of Tettigoniidae from India (Ensifera). Mitteilungen-Schweizerische Entomologische Gesellschaft, 71, 355 - 372." type="journal article" year="1998">
